author: Divya Rao
title: Photo: Rannvijay Singha’s Wife Prianka Has A Romantic Wish For His Birthday
text:
Divya Rao Mar . 18 . 2017 
Rannvijay Singha and his beautiful wife Prianka Singha welcomed an adorable little baby girl into this world a couple of weeks ago. The two named her Kainaat, and Rannvijay had the cutest explanation for it. It was the actor’s birthday recently, and Prianka took to Instagram to post this lovely message for him. Take a look. A post shared by Prianka Singha (@priankasingha) on Mar 16, 2017 at 8:35am PDT 
How sweet!
